rchitect’s conceptual sketch. The image is in a wide banner format, suitable for a website header.\",\"seed\",725449250,\"serialization_title\",\"DALL-E generation metadata\",\"sanitized\",{\"_1385\":-5,\"_1398\":1399,\"_1400\":1399,\"_1401\":1626,\"_1380\":1615,\"_1383\":1384,\"_1346\":1310},[1677],\"bc946033-c4fe-41fb-8c76-cf4ddca6bbc1\",{\"_37\":1677,\"_1328\":1679,\"_1348\":1643,\"_1324\":1687},{\"_37\":1677,\"_1330\":1680,\"_1316\":1682,\"_1336\":1683,\"_21\":1341,\"_1343\":9,\"_1334\":1686,\"_1347\":1073},{\"_1332\":1579,\"_39\":1641,\"_1334\":1681},{},1739751447.755003,{\"_1338\":550,\"_1339\":1684},[1685],\"\\nDALL·E displayed 1 images. The images are already plainly visible, so don't repeat the descriptions in detail. Do not list download links as they are available in the ChatGPT UI already. The user may download the images by clicking on them, but do not mention anything about downloading to the user.\",{\"_1385\":-5,\"_1398\":1399,\"_1400\":1399,\"_1401\":1643,\"_1380\":1615,\"_1383\":1384,\"_1346\":1310},[1688],\"0bcad703-bfef-40e3-962d-24f59ce7b135\",{\"_37\":1688,\"_1328\":1690,\"_1348\":1677,\"_1324\":1702},{\"_37\":1688,\"_1330\":1691,\"_1316\":1693,\"_1336\":1694,\"_21\":1341,\"_1342\":61,\"_1343\":9,\"_1334\":1697,\"_1347\":1073},{\"_1332\":1391,\"_1334\":1692},{},1739751447.755057,{\"_1338\":550,\"_1339\":1695},[1696],\"Aqui está a imagem do hospital em estilo sketch, como se fosse desenhada por um arquiteto famoso. A perspectiva diagonal e os traços a lápis conferem um toque profissional ao desenho, ideal para um banner no seu site. Se precisar de ajustes ou outra versão, me avise!\",{\"_1413\":1698,\"_1419\":61,\"_1420\":1700,\"_1373\":1701,\"_1385\":-5,\"_1398\":1399,\"_1400\":1399,\"_1401\":1677,\"_1380\":1615,\"_1383\":1384,\"_1346\":1310},{\"_1313\":1415,\"_1416\":1699},[1418],[],[],[1703],\"bbb211d7-5e0c-41ac-83b6-1104455621b7\",{\"_37\":1703,\"_1328\":1705,\"_1348\":1688,\"_1324\":1717},{\"_37\":1703,\"_1330\":1706,\"_1316\":1708,\"_1336\